data.description: Welcome to 88 Concord Crescent! This adorable rancher is situated on a large lot and offers 3 bedrooms, 1.5 baths, nearly 1200 square feet, hardwood floors, an abundance of natural light in the large living room, spacious dining room, attached garage, fenced backyard, and more. And don’t forget the convenient location – this property is located near Riverside Regional, Virginia Living Museum, CNU, Oyster Point, interstate access, day to day amenities, and more!
